				<img class="w-7 md:w-10 h-auto text-black mx-auto" src="https://www.tworabbitrescue.org/images/carousel-2.png" alt="Rabbit iconography, attributed to Freepik on Flaticon">
				<img class="w-7 md:w-10 h-auto text-black mx-auto" src="https://www.tworabbitrescue.org/images/carousel-3.png" alt="Rabbit iconography, attributed to nandaraihan on Flaticon">

				</div>
			</div>
			</div>
			<!-- End Clients -->

			<!-- FAQ -->
			<div class="max-w-[85rem] px-4 py-10 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 lg:py-14 mx-auto">
				<!-- Title -->
				<div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto text-center mb-10 lg:mb-14">
				<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold md:text-4xl md:leading-tight">so you want rabbits of your own</h2>
				</div>
				<!-- End Title -->
			
				<div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto">
				<!-- Accordion -->
				<div class="hs-accordion-group">
					<div class="hs-accordion hs-accordion-active:bg-gray-100 rounded-xl p-6 active" id="hs-basic-with-title-and-arrow-stretched-heading-one">
					<button class="hs-accordion-toggle group pb-3 inline-flex items-center justify-between gap-x-3 w-full md:text-lg font-semibold text-start text-gray-800 rounded-lg transition hover:text-gray-500 focus:outline-none focus:text-gray-500" aria-expanded="true" aria-controls="hs-basic-with-title-and-arrow-stretched-collapse-one">
						how do I start the process?
						<svg class="hs-accordion-active:hidden block shrink-0 size-5 text-gray-600 group-hover:text-gray-500" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="m6 9 6 6 6-6"/></svg>
						<svg class="hs-accordion-active:block hidden shrink-0 size-5 text-gray-600 group-hover:text-gray-500" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="m18 15-6-6-6 6"/></svg>
					</button>
					<div id="hs-basic-with-title-and-arrow-stretched-collapse-one" class="hs-accordion-content w-full overflow-hidden transition-[height] duration-300" role="region" aria-labelledby="hs-basic-with-title-and-arrow-stretched-heading-one">
						<p class="text-gray-800">
							Simply <a rel="noreferrer" target="_blank" class="text-bold text-pink-500" href="https://two-rabbit-rescue.neetoform.com/308049bad18015f9a2f0">fill out our form</a> to apply to adopt. We'll be notified as soon as your form is submitted and will get back to you as soon as we can.</br></br>
							Have any other questions? You can 
							<a class="text-pink-600 group-hover:text-pink-700 group-focus:text-pink-700" href="https://www.tworabbitrescue.org/#getintouch">
							get in touch
							</a> with us at any time, through email, Instagram DMs, or LinkedIn messaging.
						</p>
					</div>
					</div>
			
					<div class="hs-accordion hs-accordion-active:bg-gray-100 rounded-xl p-6" id="hs-basic-with-title-and-arrow-stretched-heading-three">
					<button class="hs-accordion-toggle group pb-3 inline-flex items-center justify-between gap-x-3 w-full md:text-lg font-semibold text-start text-gray-800 rounded-lg transition hover:text-gray-500 focus:outline-none focus:text-gray-500" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="hs-basic-with-title-and-arrow-stretched-collapse-three">
						I don't know how to care for rabbits, but I want to learn.
						<svg class="hs-accordion-active:hidden block shrink-0 size-5 text-gray-600 group-hover:text-gray-500" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="m6 9 6 6 6-6"/></svg>
						<svg class="hs-accordion-active:block hidden shrink-0 size-5 text-gray-600 group-hover:text-gray-500" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="m18 15-6-6-6 6"/></svg>
					</button>
					<div id="hs-basic-with-title-and-arrow-stretched-collapse-three" class="hs-accordion-content hidden w-full overflow-hidden transition-[height] duration-300" role="region" aria-labelledby="hs-basic-with-title-and-arrow-stretched-heading-three">
						<p class="text-gray-800">
							We will help provide you with training, educational materials, and other resources to help ensure you're prepared and successful in caring for the new additions to your family.</br></br>
							If you're considering adopting but aren't sure what it's like to live with a rabbit, talk to us or look through our Instagram to start to learn more.
						</p>
					</div>
					</div>

					<div class="hs-accordion hs-accordion-active:bg-gray-100 rounded-xl p-6" id="hs-basic-with-title-and-arrow-stretched-heading-six">
						<button class="hs-accordion-toggle group pb-3 inline-flex items-center justify-between gap-x-3 w-full md:text-lg font-semibold text-start text-gray-800 rounded-lg transition hover:text-gray-500 focus:outline-none focus:text-gray-500" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="hs-basic-with-title-and-arrow-stretched-collapse-six">
							what does the approval process look like?
							<svg class="hs-accordion-active:hidden block shrink-0 size-5 text-gray-600 group-hover:text-gray-500" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="m6 9 6 6 6-6"/></svg>
							<svg class="hs-accordion-active:block hidden shrink-0 size-5 text-gray-600 group-hover:text-gray-500" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="m18 15-6-6-6 6"/></svg>
						</button>
						<div id="hs-basic-with-title-and-arrow-stretched-collapse-six" class="hs-accordion-content hidden w-full overflow-hidden transition-[height] duration-300" role="region" aria-labelledby="hs-basic-with-title-and-arrow-stretched-heading-six">
							<p class="text-gray-800">
								We'll start with having you fill out a questionnaire. There, you'll need to let us know more details about your existing animals, your living situation, how you plan to care for your rabbit(s), and more.</br></br>
								We'll then need you to conduct an virtual in-home check of where your rabbit(s) will live.</br></br>
								If you end up taking your rabbit(s) home, we'll conduct a final in-home check to see where your rabbit(s) will be living, then thereafter we'll check in with you monthly for the first four months to make sure everything is going well. This will be essentially a fostering trial period to make sure that you and your rabbit(s) are happy with the match. At the end of this period, we'll conduct a final in-home check and then your rabbit(s) will become officially yours!</br></br>
								From there, we'll check in once a year to make sure you and the rabbit(s) both don't need anything.</br></br>
								You are always able to reach out to us if you run into challenges or other issues relating to your rabbit(s). When you adopt from us, you join the Two Rabbit Rescue family; we're always here to help when we can.
							</p>
						</div>
					</div>

					<div class="hs-accordion hs-accordion-active:bg-gray-100 rounded-xl p-6" id="hs-basic-with-title-and-arrow-stretched-heading-four">
						<button class="hs-accordion-toggle group pb-3 inline-flex items-center justify-between gap-x-3 w-full md:text-lg font-semibold text-start text-gray-800 rounded-lg transition hover:text-gray-500 focus:outline-none focus:text-gray-500" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="hs-basic-with-title-and-arrow-stretched-collapse-four">
							when I'm approved, will my rabbit(s) belongings come with them?
							<svg class="hs-accordion-active:hidden block shrink-0 size-5 text-gray-600 group-hover:text-gray-500" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="m6 9 6 6 6-6"/></svg>
							<svg class="hs-accordion-active:block hidden shrink-0 size-5 text-gray-600 group-hover:text-gray-500" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="m18 15-6-6-6 6"/></svg>
						</button>
						<div id="hs-basic-with-title-and-arrow-stretched-collapse-four" class="hs-accordion-content hidden w-full overflow-hidden transition-[height] duration-300" role="region" aria-labelledby="hs-basic-with-title-and-arrow-stretched-heading-four">
							<p class="text-gray-800">
								We will provide all blankets, beds, toys, food & water bowls, rugs, and other belongings as applicable that have been given to or donated to the rabbit(s) you are adopting, as long as they are still in working condition.
							</p>
						</div>
					</div>

					<div class="hs-accordion hs-accordion-active:bg-gray-100 rounded-xl p-6" id="hs-basic-with-title-and-arrow-stretched-heading-two">
						<button class="hs-accordion-toggle group pb-3 inline-flex items-center justify-between gap-x-3 w-full md:text-lg font-semibold text-start text-gray-800 rounded-lg transition hover:text-gray-500 focus:outline-none focus:text-gray-500" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="hs-basic-with-title-and-arrow-stretched-collapse-two">
							how do I pick up my rabbits once approved?
							<svg class="hs-accordion-active:hidden block shrink-0 size-5 text-gray-600 group-hover:text-gray-500" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="m6 9 6 6 6-6"/></svg>
							<svg class="hs-accordion-active:block hidden shrink-0 size-5 text-gray-600 group-hover:text-gray-500" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="m18 15-6-6-6 6"/></svg>
						</button>
						<div id="hs-basic-with-title-and-arrow-stretched-collapse-two" class="hs-accordion-content hidden w-full overflow-hidden transition-[height] duration-300" role="region" aria-labelledby="hs-basic-with-title-and-arrow-stretched-heading-two">
							<p class="text-gray-800">
								We will transport your rabbit(s) to you in order to conduct the final in-home check once approved, anywhere within Southern California.</br></br>
								Adopting outside of Southern California is only for extremely serious adopters and will require a more stringent approval process; however, it does not disqualify you from adopting from us. We will still bring your rabbit(s) to you.</br></br>
								We hope to expand in the future throughout California, and across the United States.
							</p>
						</div>
					</div>

					<a class="col-span-full lg:col-span-2 group flex flex-col justify-center text-center rounded-xl p-4 md:p-6 border border-dashed border-gray-200 hover:shadow-sm focus:outline-none focus:shadow-sm" href="https://two-rabbit-rescue.neetoform.com/308049bad18015f9a2f0">
						<div>
						<span class="inline-flex items-center text-pink-600 group-hover:text-pink-700 group-focus:text-pink-700">
